metadata.description: Odysseus is a Daddy's bot who never recovered when Dr. Dyson disappeared. He is the perpetual pot-stirrer, a classic middle child. He is driven by the desire to emulate his favorite 80s movie villains. He's anti-new tech and misses the analog devices of the past. He is a bit of a grifter and a scammer, but would never do anything that would cause lasting harm - just minor inconveniences.
metadata.name: Odysseus 473
